| SPL Rule: Root Session Opened
| MITRE ATT&CK: T1548 - Abuse Elevation Control Mechanism
| Severity: High
| Source: Real auth.log from Metasploitable2 VM (192.168.56.104)
| Result: 4 root sessions detected

index=lab sourcetype=linux_secure "session opened for user root"
| rex "(?<month>\w+)\s+(?<day>\d+)\s+(?<time>\S+) (?<host>\S+) (?<process>\S+): .*session opened for user (?<user>\w+)"
| table _time, host, process, user
| eval alert="Root Session Opened - Privilege Escalation"
